name: May Thet Htar Swe
description: '''May Thet Htar Swe''' ({{langx|my|မေသက်ထားဆွေ}}; born 10 January 2003) is a traditional [[Burmese people|Burmese]] [[Mahāgīta|classical]], [[Country music|country]], and [[dhamma]] singer. She began her career as a child, and is known both for her mastery of songs from the Burmese classical tradition and her musical versatility, which spans several genres.
